        <abstract>
            <p>Describes Tierra del Fuego and Cape Horn; was reminded of hours at Barmouth; chafes at the length of the trip.</p>
            <p>Hopes the Whigs will do away with slavery – has seen enough of it and Negroes to be disgusted with the lies heard in England.</p>
        </abstract>
